text: Saint-Agnan-le-Malherbe is a former commune. It is found in the Normandy region in the Calvados department in the northwest of France. On 1 January 2016, it was merged into the new commune of Malherbe-sur-Ajon.Arrêté préfectoral 9 December 2015 == References == Category:Former communes in Calvados
title: Saint-Agnan-le-Malherbe
